title: PIIE's Kirkegaard: Brexit Won't Damage Europe Economy (Audio)
itunes:title: PIIE's Kirkegaard: Brexit Won't Damage Europe Economy (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Jacob Kirkegaard, Senior Fellow at the Peterson Institute for International Economics, on whether the strong UK retail sales and jobs report are reflecting the impact of Brexit to the UK economy.
